    "MeasureNumber": 2477,
    "CatchLine": "Requires purchaser of real property with intent to acquire redemption rights to include warning in deed transferring property.",
    "MinorityCatchLine": null,
    "MeasureSummary": "\tRequires purchaser of real property with intent to acquire redemption rights to include warning in deed transferring property. \n\tRequires sheriff to include in notice of execution sale posted on website notice regarding certain rights of debtors. \n\tRequires person filing complaint to foreclose residential trust deed to provide lien debtor with notice about sale of redemption rights. Revises notice required in nonjudicial foreclosure for consistency.",
